    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains pristine, smelling like new and showing zero wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with every system functioning exactly as intended and a complete service history to document its meticulous care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment and remains in 'as-new' condition for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
