      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster. Meticulously preserved and mechanically peerless, this unit represents a premier opportunity for the serious enthusiast seeking a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree and distinction.",
      "price": 46500.0,
